>\n                                <div class=\"tposition\">助理研究员</div>\n                                <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                                <div class=\"tcontent\">\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>博士、助理研究员</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p>邮  箱: heli529@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                  <p></p>\n                                   <p></p>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                        </div>\n    </div>\n    <ul class=\"right-column-menu tright-column-menu\">  \n                     \n       <li class=\"on\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">教育背景</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">工作经历</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究领域</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">研究概况</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术成果</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">奖励与荣誉</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n    </ul> \n    \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-on\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2015-2016<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>同方威视联合清华大学 博士后</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2016-2023 &nbsp;同方威视科技有限公司 电子工程师</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2023至今 清华大学工程物理系 助理研究员</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n</div></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(50, 50, 50);\">● </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">2023-</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">至今</span><span style=\"text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;;\">　</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">清华大学工程物理系</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">助理研究员</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: rgb(50, 50, 50);\">● </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2016-2023&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">同方威视科技有限公司 电子工程师</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2015-2016<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">　</span>同方威视联合清华大学 博士后</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>博士后及工作期间：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1.低温低噪声低本底专用集成电路（ASIC）测试与集成。这部分工作是为中国暗物质实验（CDEX）中使用的高纯锗探测器集成与测试ASIC前端电子学。工作内容包括ASIC的噪声优化测试，前端电子学系统的设计与测试，前端电子学低本底材料的选择与验证。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. 高纯锗探测器前端电子学研发。由于高纯锗探测器是目前已知能量分辨率最高到的半导体探测器，在核电、环保、国土安全等领域都有着广泛的应用。这部分的主要工作内容有：自主研发低噪声前端电子学，保证探测器性能；研发高计数率前放，保证在高强度射线应用场景下探测器信号依旧能正常读出；研发具有较强电磁干扰免疫能力的前端电子学，保证在电制冷应用场景下，探测器性能不会过多劣化。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>博士研究生期间：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1.微结构气体探测器专用集成电路研发。微结构气体探测器往往需要多通道电子学读出，同时电子学系统及功耗都有一定要求，采用专用集成电路（ASIC）是目前国际上同类研究的趋势。这部分工作主要就是为不同应用的微结构气体探测器，如GEM、Micro-megas，针对其应用及读出信号特征设计和测试ASIC。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. TPC读出信号的数字信号处理方法研究。功耗及系统稳定性的限制，一般在气体探测器读出电子学中不会设计太高带宽的前端电子学，但部分应用对于信号的带宽又有着较高的需求，此时可以通过将采集到的数据反卷积的办法将信号恢复回高带宽。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2015至今高纯锗谱仪前端低噪声电子学研发：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. 自主研发应用谱仪中的同轴型高纯锗探测器读出的前端电子学，保障了探测器的高分辨率性能，成功取代了国外的读出芯片。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. 设计与研发了高计数前端电子学，在高强度射线应用环境下，各项测试指标不逊于国际上同类产品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. 设计与优化了具有较高抗电磁干扰能力的前端电子学，保证了在纯电制冷的应用中电磁干扰及振动不会过分劣化高纯锗探测器的能量分辨率性能。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2015至今CDEX 低温低本底前端 ASIC 研究及测试：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. 测试和验证应用点电极高纯锗探测器读出的专用集成电路。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. 设计和搭建低噪声</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">ASIC测试环境</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. 前端电子学低本底材料调研及验证。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2010-2015 &nbsp;nTPC 前端读出多通道ASIC 研发</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. 设计并实现了应用nTPC的专用集成电路CASAGEM，该芯片集成了16个读出通道，且每个通道都能实现低噪声前端电荷灵敏放大以及5阶信号成形。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. 配合系统联调，解决测试过程中遇到的各类电子学问题。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br></span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>发表论文：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. H Li, D zhi, Y Li etc. CASAGEM: Areadout ASIC for MPGDs, 2012 IEEE NSS/MIC Conference Record, 2012EI</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. &nbsp;Li He, Zhi D, Yulan L. Development of amulti-channel readout ASIC for a fast neutron spectrometer based on GEM-TPC.Chinese Physics C, 2014SCI</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. L.He, Z.Deng,H.Li etc. The digitalpenalized LMS deconvolution method for TPC X-ray polarimeter signal processing.Journal of Instrumentation,2015 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SCI</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4. Li He, Jiajun Hao, Zhi Deng etc.Comparison of JFET／MOS／HEMT Based Low Noise Charge SensitivePreamplifiers for HPGe Detectors in Cryogenic Temperature, The 13th Workshop onLow Temperature Electronics, 2018 &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">5. Zhi Deng, Li He, Feng Liu etc. Development ofcryogenic CMOS Readout ASICs for the Point-Contact HPGe Detectors for DarkMatter Search and Neutrino Experiments, The 12th Workshop on Low TemperatureElectronics, 2017 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">6. Z.Deng, L.He, Fliu etc. An Ultra-Low NoiseCryogenic CMOS Charge Sensitive Preamplifier for Large Volume Point-ContactHPGe Detectors，Journal of Instrumentation, 2018 &nbsp; SCI</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">7. J.Hao, L.He, Z.Deng. A cryogeniclow-background low-noise CMOS preamplifier for HPGe detectors. Journal ofInstrumentation,2022 &nbsp; &nbsp;SCI</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">8. F Liu，Z Deng，L He，Y Liu. Development of the full-chain cryogenic readout electronicsfor the point-contact HPGe detectors. Nuclear Instruments &amp; Methods inPhysics Research, 2019 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;EI</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">9. Hao J, Deng Z, He L, et al. A Cryogenic CMOSPreamplifier with Very Large Dynamic Range for HPGe Detectors. [C]//2020 IEEENSS/MIC. 1-4EI</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>参与专利</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">1. 集成电路布图设计 CASAGEM 芯片，何力</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2. 一种基于阴极波形采样的像素型碲锌镉半导体探测系统。发明人：李玉兰；付逸冬；杨剑；张立钦；何力；于海军；李秀霞</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">3. 数字多道谱仪。发明人：李红；李玉兰；张智；何力；常建平；于海军；位红燕；李秀霞</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">4. 一种用于高纯锗探测器的低振动免维护零蒸发低温恒温器。发明人：李玉兰、常建平、于海军、李秀霞、李红、何力</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap;\">● </span>2017年 北京市博士后科研活动经费资助 二等</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div class=\"links-box\">\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:20px;\"></div>\n            <div class=\"model-title\">\n                <div class=\"model\">常用链接</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"model-block\"></div>\n            <ul>\n      <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74493)\"><li>清华大学</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://news.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74494)\"><li>清华新闻网</li></a>\n    <a href=\"https://tsinghua.cn.libguides.com/c.php?g=915369\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1746825595, 74495)\"><li>图书馆－核学科</li></a>\n</ul>\n            <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:41px;\"></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"copy-right-box\">\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:26px;\"></div>\n        <ul>\n            <script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/mp4video.js\"></script>\n<li>地址：清华大学工程物理系（刘卿楼）</li> \n<li>邮编：100084</li> \n<li>电话：010-62785727</li> \n<li>邮箱：gwbgs@mail.tsinghua.edu.cn</li>\n        </ul>\n        <div style=\"width:100%;height:10px;\"></div>\n        <!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<div class=\"copy-right\">Copyright <span>©</span> 2020 清华大学工程物理系 All Right Reserved&nbsp;<script type=\"text/javascript\">var cnzz_protocol = ((\"https:\" == document.location.protocol) ? \"https://\" : \"http://\");document.write(unescape(\"%3Cspan id='cnzz_stat_icon_1277133078'%3E%3C/span%3E%3Cscript src='\" + cnzz_protocol + \"s5.cnzz.com/z_stat.php%3Fid%3D1277133078%26show%3Dpic' type='text/javascript'%3E%3C/script%3E\"));</script><span id=\"cnzz_stat_icon_1277133078\"></span><script src=\"https://s5.cnzz.com/z_stat.php?id=1277133078&amp;show=pic\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script></div>\n    </div>\n  <!--底部-- end-->\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<script>\n\n$('.right-column-box .right-column-menu li:first .text').text() == '' && $('.right-column-box .right-column-menu li:first').remove();\n\n$('.right-column-box .right-column-menu li:first').addClass('on');\n</script>\n\n\n</body></html>"
